impact of the results, in profound ways, transcend the P&L. =E2=80=9CI thin=
k we can call another winner in the streaming wars,=E2=80=9D Matt wrote. =
=E2=80=9CNetflix, obviously, is already one of the three or four video serv=
ices that will survive this era of digital transition. YouTube is there, to=
o. Spotify, if we count audio. And now, Disney almost certainly will make i=
t.=E2=80=9D Indeed, this battle to survive until the next stage of the indu=
stry is far more consequential than any sporting contest. It=E2=80=99s the =
story of our time, and the macro-saga of our industry. And it=E2=80=99s cer=
